4
00:00:51.529 --> 00:00:54.209
- How?
- It's just all wrong.


5
00:00:54.290 --> 00:00:58.010
- Wrong?
- I've made up my mind, this is it.


6
00:00:58.090 --> 00:01:02.129
- Was it ever right?
- Don't tell anyone anything.


7
00:05:37.729 --> 00:05:42.849
Sasha, are you sleeping?
I brought you some food.


8
00:05:44.250 --> 00:05:45.609
How was work?

9
00:05:46.049 --> 00:05:52.570
