Hopefully not.


12
00:06:00.049 --> 00:06:03.369
Don't worry,
we'll figure something out.


13
00:06:05.690 --> 00:06:07.770
Why do you look so pale?

14
00:06:10.609 --> 00:06:14.090
I've been throwing up all night.
It was probably the food you brought.


15
00:06:14.570 --> 00:06:16.969
Don't make me laugh. Please.

16
00:06:17.969 --> 00:06:22.570
You've been home all week.
Go somewhere, get out of the house.


17
00:06:27.650 --> 00:06:31.729
Ok then. I hate working
the night shift. I'm going to bed.


18
00:06:31.810 --> 00:06:35.010
Reheat the cereal and meatballs
I brought. It's delicious.


19
00:06:35.330 --> 00:06:36.690
