20
00:07:24.450 --> 00:07:26.810
- Anything to drink?
- Vodka.


21
00:07:27.529 --> 00:07:30.729
- How much? A shot?
- Double!


22
00:07:37.529 --> 00:07:39.049
200 rubles.

23
00:07:45.169 --> 00:07:47.250
Give us two more, sweetie.

24
00:07:52.890 --> 00:07:55.409
I haven't seen you here before.

25
00:09:38.090 --> 00:09:40.290
Come on, let's do it.

26
00:09:50.810 --> 00:09:54.570
Everyone face down
and get your hands up! Fast!


27
00:09:54.649 --> 00:09:56.690
Hands behind your head!

28
00:10:05.290 --> 00:10:07.450
Check their passports.

29
00:10:07.530 --> 00:10:09.729
Show me your ID's, now!

30
00:10:09.810 --> 00:10:11.969
How many are in here?

31
00:10:15.290 --> 00:10:18.930
Eleven fucking faggots,
can you believe this shit?


32
00:10:39.889 --> 00:10:40.969
- Hello?
- Dima!


33
00:10:41.050 --> 00:10:42.769
Yes, what happened?

34
00:10:42.849 --> 00:10:45.050
Mom told me something
is wrong with grandma.


35
00:10:45.129 --> 00:10:47.489
She hasn't been answering
her phone for a week.


36
00:10:47.570 --> 00:10:50.889
- Don't worry, she's fine.
- It's been seven days already.


37
00:10:50.969 --> 00:10:53.649
- She always calls back...
- I don't know, we should go visit her.


38
00:10:53.729 --> 00:10:56.810
Can you take off work?
I can't leave him.


39
00:10:56.889 --> 00:10:58.410
I'll try.

40
00:10:58.489 --> 00:11:02.249
- Find out what's wrong with grandma.
- Ok, I'll do my best.


41
00:11:02.330 --> 00:11:05.729
Mom will be coming over tonight.
I have to run, love you.


42
00:11:05.810 --> 00:11:07.090
Bye.

43
00:11:28.369 --> 00:11:31.050
- Dima, what's up.
- Ah, it's you.


44
00:11:32.489 --> 00:11:35.170
What should we do
with those faggots?


45
00:11:35.769 --> 00:11:39.410
- I don't know, why?
- Should we press charges or what?


46
00:11:39.489 --> 00:11:43.769
- How many are there again?
- Eleven.


47
00:11:45.570 --> 00:11:47.290
Two chicks, too.

48
00:12:00.330 --> 00:12:03.810
- Are you ok?
- Yes.


49
00:12:07.489 --> 00:12:12.050
