on the same street as him.


53
00:12:33.249 --> 00:12:36.609
- By the way, he...
- Listen, Anna just called.


54
00:12:39.810 --> 00:12:44.769
Some family problem.
I might call out on Monday.


55
00:12:44.849 --> 00:12:48.930
- Can you cover me?
- Of course brother, no worries.


56
00:12:52.489 --> 00:12:54.489
