And you can take some for the road.


96
00:17:16.169 --> 00:17:21.490
- I don't know why, but I feel weird.
- Why?


97
00:17:22.090 --> 00:17:25.409
I don't know, I've gota strange
feeling in my gut.


98
00:17:26.090 --> 00:17:28.929
