103
00:17:46.770 --> 00:17:49.649
- Can you talk to him?
- About what?


104
00:17:50.369 --> 00:17:53.970
Try to ask him, maybe you can find
something out.


105
00:17:54.050 --> 00:17:59.250
- He doesn't tell me anything.
- Ok, I will ask.


106
00:18:04.010 --> 00:18:07.689
- Forgive me.
