133
00:28:32.050 --> 00:28:33.369
Yes.

134
00:28:36.209 --> 00:28:39.609
- I can't explain.
- I can't look in her eyes anymore.


135
00:28:39.689 --> 00:28:43.770
Do you understand?
I can't lie to her anymore.


136
00:28:46.050 --> 00:28:48.330
I can't eat or drink.

137
00:28:49.570 --> 00:28:52.050
I don't know what is happening with me.

138
00:28:55.010 --> 00:28:56.810
All these feelings.

139
00:29:19.730 --> 00:29:21.649
It's time to go.

140
00:34:22.169 --> 00:34:23.769
What's wrong?

141
00:34:24.689 --> 00:34:26.129
