142
00:34:27.890 --> 00:34:32.169
Tell me, what's wrong?

143
00:34:37.010 --> 00:34:38.530
Asshole.

144
00:34:55.050 --> 00:34:59.169
This is a really good one.
Your mom packed it for us.


145
00:35:04.249 --> 00:35:06.209
She makes the best one.

146
00:35:09.329 --> 00:35:10.970
