160
00:38:19.410 --> 00:38:23.609
I'd do it the same way again.

161
00:38:26.129 --> 00:38:29.689
It's all good. Honestly.

162
00:38:35.209 --> 00:38:36.769
I love you.

163
00:40:02.530 --> 00:40:04.649
I used to come here a lot.

164
00:40:05.450 --> 00:40:08.329
- What for?
